    STEP 7:- else if(sales >= 20000 && Sales < 30000)
                        profit=(500+(sales/100)*9);
    STEP 8:- else if(sales >= 10000 && Sales < 20000)
                        profit=(450+(sales/100)*5);
    STEP 5:- else(sales < 10000)
                        profit=(400+(sales/100)*3);
    STEP 6:- Print profit.
    STEP 7:- End

